entries.title: Arkane Studios
entries.description:
Founded in 1999, Arkane® Studios has grown to become one of the most renowned and critically acclaimed development teams in the video game industry. With teams located in Lyon, France, and Austin, Texas, Arkane has earned a reputation for creating games with unique style, immersive action, and a hand-crafted approach. The studio’s titles, which include __Dishonored®, Dishonored 2,__ and __Prey®,__ have won hundreds of prestigious accolades around the globe, including several "Game of the Year" awards.

__DEATHLOOP™__ by Arkane Lyon and helmed by Arkane veterans Dinga Bakaba (Game Director) and Sebastien Mitton (Art Director), is now available on PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S and PC. Arkane Austin is currently developing the upcoming title __Redfall™__, led by Studio/Creative Director Harvey Smith and Co-Creative Director Ricardo Bare. Coming May 2, 2023, Redfall will release exclusively on Xbox Series X|S and PC and will be available day one on Xbox Game Pass.
